WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:01.040
Good morning family.

00:00:01.040 --> 00:00:02.627
How are y'all doing today?

00:00:02.627 --> 00:00:04.467
I'm excited to be with you.

00:00:04.467 --> 00:00:07.210
I have some things on my heart to talk to you about.

00:00:07.595 --> 00:00:15.851
I went to a church service last night and it was amazing—exactly what I'm looking for.

00:00:16.246 --> 00:00:23.880
The Spirit of the Lord moved, and the presence of the Lord was so amazing.

00:00:23.880 --> 00:00:27.991
The atmosphere was charged with His glory.

00:00:28.996 --> 00:00:31.444
I just want to tell you about it a little bit.

00:00:32.056 --> 00:00:33.973
My son went and he got a touch from the Lord.

00:00:33.973 --> 00:00:35.160
My wife—we all were blessed.

00:00:35.160 --> 00:00:37.500
We were blessed by this church service.

00:00:38.054 --> 00:00:44.395
It's nice to just go in there and get to drink, get refreshed.

00:00:45.789 --> 00:00:47.173
It was just awesome.

00:00:47.173 --> 00:00:49.994
I know there's many more to come.

00:00:50.920 --> 00:00:58.691
Collinsville, Oklahoma is the Hiding Place; I'm telling y'all, Jesus is doing something huge at Collinsville, Oklahoma.

00:01:03.258 --> 00:01:03.649
I'm just human.

00:01:03.649 --> 00:01:04.940
Like I said, I'm just real with you.

00:01:09.085 --> 00:01:12.093
I've got issues and I work through them.

00:01:12.093 --> 00:01:14.726
We work out our salvation with fear and trembling.

00:01:14.726 --> 00:01:18.800
I try every single day to walk the best I can.

00:01:20.600 --> 00:01:23.017
I'm hungry and thirsty just like everybody else.

00:01:23.320 --> 00:01:25.920
I sit in the back and I just want to be a sponge.

00:01:25.920 --> 00:01:34.220
I sit in the very back row a lot of times and I just watch and see if I see any angelics or angelic visitations.

00:01:35.733 --> 00:01:44.591
I don't go to the front; a lot of times I like to see if there's ministering spirits coming in to bless the congregation, because that's what happens a lot.

00:01:45.267 --> 00:01:49.685
In this case, I was just worshiping because the worship was phenomenal.

00:01:49.685 --> 00:01:53.849
The glory of the Lord came in with the worship.

00:01:54.640 --> 00:02:00.484
I was sitting in the back, like I said, and I had my head down and all of a sudden Jesus appeared to me in an open-eyed vision.

00:02:03.897 --> 00:02:07.858
He came to me and he was this close—this close to me.

00:02:08.209 --> 00:02:16.720
He was just observing me, but he was smiling; he had a huge smile on his face, like he was laughing, and he was just enjoying the service.

00:02:17.080 --> 00:02:18.760
He was looking down at me.

00:02:19.479 --> 00:02:24.665
He never spoke, but all of a sudden I was in the Spirit.

00:02:25.800 --> 00:02:29.128
I looked down and I saw a crown—a beautiful crown full of rubies.

00:02:37.626 --> 00:02:43.336
It had diamonds all around this onyx-looking stone.

00:02:44.890 --> 00:02:47.564
My first initial thought was, 'Wow, onyx is dark.

00:02:48.186 --> 00:02:49.500
It's a black stone.

00:02:49.880 --> 00:02:51.399
That's kind of evil.

00:02:51.399 --> 00:02:56.640
' But the Lord heard my thoughts and He spoke to me.

00:02:57.227 --> 00:03:01.795
He said, 'Brandon, I created all colors.

00:03:02.280 --> 00:03:05.536
I created everything richly for you to enjoy, son.

00:03:05.536 --> 00:03:09.812
Black onyx—I made that stone; it's here from Me.

00:03:09.812 --> 00:03:18.194
' I was blessed by what He said because it changed my opinion about black onyx stone.

00:03:18.804 --> 00:03:30.120
I was looking at this crown, but standing in front of the King of Kings, my heart instantaneously was like, 'Oh, I want to give You something.

00:03:30.120 --> 00:03:31.862
I want to honor You with something.

00:03:31.862 --> 00:03:35.987
' I looked down and I didn't have anything on me other than just me.

00:03:38.013 --> 00:03:43.699
I thought I'd just give Him me, but I was like, 'I want to give more' because I'm standing in front of the King of Kings.

00:03:44.007 --> 00:03:47.190
In the vision, I picked up that beautiful crown.

00:03:47.580 --> 00:03:54.250
It had diamonds wrapped around each one of those onyx stones, and there were humongous diamonds all on this.

00:03:54.460 --> 00:03:56.080
He said, 'This is your personal crown.

00:03:56.080 --> 00:04:02.143
Every one of my children will have a crown—your personal crown—when they come to heaven.

00:04:02.143 --> 00:04:08.207
' It was beautiful; there were all kinds of cool things in that crown.

00:04:09.847 --> 00:04:24.700
He told me He had a crown that's designed for each individual believer; it's made special for them with the jewels, and everything represents something.

00:04:25.860 --> 00:04:31.560
I picked up that crown and all I could do was worship Him with it by giving it to Him.

00:04:33.916 --> 00:04:37.700
I took that crown in the Spirit and I handed it over to Him.

00:04:37.880 --> 00:04:40.079
I was just like, 'I just want to give You an offering.

00:04:40.079 --> 00:04:42.754
I just want to give You something special.

00:04:42.754 --> 00:04:54.291
' When you're entering into the presence of a king, I wanted to bring Him a gift like the wise men brought Him gold, myrrh, and frankincense.

00:04:55.029 --> 00:04:59.387
They brought Him the gifts because they were worshiping Him with them.

00:04:59.671 --> 00:05:01.611
I thought it was so beautiful.

00:05:05.298 --> 00:05:05.582
I was casting down the golden crowns there.

00:05:07.017 --> 00:05:13.590
I picked it up in the Spirit, in the open-eyed vision, and I handed it to Him.

00:05:17.235 --> 00:05:23.218
That scripture, 'casting down the golden crowns'—I didn't have the whole scripture of it, but I know it's in Revelation, I believe.

00:05:24.453 --> 00:05:27.588
It just echoed inside of me, and I blessed Him with it.

00:05:27.588 --> 00:05:32.120
All He did was just smile with this love on His face.

00:05:44.640 --> 00:05:44.940
It was such an honor.

00:05:45.578 --> 00:05:57.369
He received from me, but I was like, 'I have nothing of my own to give You, Lord, other than just me.

00:05:57.369 --> 00:06:06.439
' But I gave Him a gift out of something that He blessed me with.

00:06:06.439 --> 00:06:17.304
Then He spoke to me and said, 'Brandon, I'm bringing a refreshing to my people.

00:06:17.304 --> 00:06:20.280
They're thirsty.

00:06:20.280 --> 00:06:34.454
' There's many of you watching this video today that are thirsty for a fresh drink of that living water.

00:06:34.454 --> 00:06:47.751
At this moment, waves of His glory in that vision—whenever I looked over and across the front of the church—there were waves of His glory, waves of His presence rolling in.

00:06:47.751 --> 00:06:54.582
I could see a beautiful pink, like a sunset, with all kinds of beautiful pink colors.

00:06:56.160 --> 00:07:03.907
The waves, when they were coming in, looked like they were glowing with this pink sunset color.

00:07:03.907 --> 00:07:09.764
They were coming over the people and bringing a refreshing.

00:07:29.140 --> 00:07:29.573
The Lord said, 'I'm going to bring a refreshing over my remnant, over my people that are seeking Me.

00:07:29.573 --> 00:07:45.813
' I could see the waves coming in, and He said, 'As that wave comes in, I'm going to bring another one right on the heels of it.

00:07:45.813 --> 00:08:01.852
' In these last days, if you stay close to the vine, if you abide in Me and My words remain in you, a continual refreshing...

00:08:06.599 --> 00:08:09.520
you shall ask what you will and it shall be done.

00:08:09.520 --> 00:08:23.090
He said, 'I'm bringing a wave of my glory upon my people—a wave of refreshing, a continual refreshing—by drinking from that cup.

00:08:23.090 --> 00:08:33.450
' When I talk about 'Fill my cup, Lord, I lift it up, Lord, come and quench,' that's what I'm talking about—drinking from that river of living water.

00:08:45.329 --> 00:08:45.578
He said out of your belly shall flow rivers of living water.

00:08:45.578 --> 00:08:58.509
I'm telling you, there's a river of living water that's going to start to bubble out of you as you stay close to Him and you seek Him daily.

00:08:58.509 --> 00:09:02.959
He's going to bring a refreshing over you.

00:09:02.959 --> 00:09:10.440
So I'm going to believe God with you today for a fresh drink of that water.

00:09:10.440 --> 00:09:24.300
Jesus wants to become real to those in a place of desperation—those who are so hungry and thirsty and desperate for Him to touch you in a mighty way.

00:09:26.620 --> 00:09:39.943
I'm telling you, Jesus wants to become real to you and become that fresh drink for you so that you're not dry and you're not burned out.

00:09:39.943 --> 00:10:04.057
There's a lot of you that are wanting to give up on things—wanting to give up on ministry, your marriage, your children, your jobs, whatever—saying, 'I can't take the pressure anymore; this has become too hard to keep going through.

00:10:04.057 --> 00:10:07.404
' The Lord wants to give you a fresh touch today.

00:10:17.555 --> 00:10:17.870
He told me, 'Brandon, I want to give my people a drink.

00:10:17.870 --> 00:10:33.219
' There's a lot of you in that desperation of saying, 'Hey, I've been battling this sickness, this disease, this depression, anxiety, or fear.

00:10:33.219 --> 00:10:36.640
How can I get through this?

00:10:36.640 --> 00:10:39.006
I can't go anymore.

00:10:39.006 --> 00:10:45.150
' You keep rehearsing it: 'God, where are You?

00:10:45.150 --> 00:10:49.266
How can I get through this?

00:10:49.266 --> 00:11:01.080
' But I'm telling you, the Lord told me last night, 'I want to bring a fresh touch on my people,' and He wants to bring it now.

00:11:01.080 --> 00:11:06.800
I was sitting there, and like I said, I deal with my own things.

00:11:06.800 --> 00:11:14.074
I was believing maybe next service I'll get my breakthrough for what I'm believing for—for my daughter, Megan.

00:11:14.074 --> 00:11:22.251
Maybe next time I'm in church, maybe Megan will get her full manifestation.

00:11:22.251 --> 00:11:28.720
Maybe I'll get my full manifestation of things that I'm believing for.

00:11:30.959 --> 00:11:39.206
The Lord stopped me in that same vision, in that same experience, and said, 'Brandon, why not now?

00:11:39.206 --> 00:11:49.940
Why do you always push off the miracle for tomorrow when I'm ready to do it now?

00:11:49.940 --> 00:11:55.330
' Faith calls those things that be not as though they are—right now.

00:11:55.330 --> 00:11:59.497
Why do I always push off the miracle?

00:11:59.497 --> 00:12:02.130
Faith calls it now.

00:12:05.699 --> 00:12:12.847
The Lord's not always telling you it's tomorrow—that in the 'sweet by and by' you're going to get it.

00:12:12.847 --> 00:12:15.227
Receive it now.

00:12:15.227 --> 00:12:34.165
Abraham staggered not at the promise of God through unbelief, but he was strong in faith, believing and fully persuaded that what God had promised, He was able also to perform it.

00:12:39.110 --> 00:12:40.140
I want you to believe right now in your circumstances for your 'now.

00:12:40.140 --> 00:12:51.108
' Now faith is the substance of things hoped for and evidence of things not seen.

00:12:51.108 --> 00:13:01.857
'Now' is the things you're believing for—not tomorrow, not next service, not when you get around another healing minister.

00:13:10.949 --> 00:13:11.331
Believe for your manifestation today.

00:13:11.331 --> 00:13:24.178
I'm always having thoughts like, 'Maybe next time, maybe a year from now, maybe my breakthrough will come.

00:13:24.178 --> 00:13:34.879
' You're always kicking that can down the road that God's going to do something.

00:13:34.879 --> 00:13:43.394
But we're going to believe God for today for your miracle.

00:13:43.394 --> 00:14:00.895
We're going to believe God today for your fresh touch—for a drink that will fill your cup because you're lifting it up and quench the thirsting of your soul.

00:14:12.608 --> 00:14:12.959
I believe with all my heart Jesus is the restorer of all things, that nothing is impossible for Him.

00:14:12.959 --> 00:14:18.509
Whatever you put your hands to will prosper.

00:14:18.509 --> 00:14:26.133
Whatever you touch will be blessed because you're a child of the King.

00:14:26.133 --> 00:14:33.415
Greater is He that is in you than he that is in the world.

00:14:33.415 --> 00:14:44.700
A thousand shall fall at your side and ten thousand at your right hand, but nothing shall come nigh.

00:14:44.700 --> 00:14:58.840
I believe with all my heart Jesus paid the price for you to walk in victory from sickness and disease, from bondage, from addictions.

00:14:58.840 --> 00:15:09.044
It doesn't matter what you're going through; there's nothing too hard that Jesus can't set you free from.

00:15:23.139 --> 00:15:23.449
I believe today is your day.

00:15:23.449 --> 00:15:26.860
Today is your day for your miracle.

00:15:26.860 --> 00:15:30.406
So let's believe right now together.

00:15:30.406 --> 00:15:39.645
Whatever you're believing for, no matter how big it may seem in your mind, Jesus knows what you need.

00:15:39.645 --> 00:15:44.593
I'll come in agreement with you and believe for your manifestation.

00:15:50.190 --> 00:15:50.495
Father, I thank You for every need.

00:15:52.275 --> 00:15:54.484
I come in agreement with these people right now.

00:16:11.255 --> 00:16:14.293
We are healed now.

00:16:14.293 --> 00:16:18.187
Nothing's too big, nothing's too small.

00:16:20.230 --> 00:16:27.180
Jesus, I thank You that You said by Your stripes we are healed.

00:16:37.906 --> 00:16:44.240
We call them healed now—not tomorrow, not the next day—but now.

00:16:45.940 --> 00:16:52.119
We call them healed now in Jesus' name.

00:17:01.569 --> 00:17:03.692
We receive healing over every single circumstance—healing and deliverance from addictions, sickness, disease, cancer, diabetes, heart disease, lung disease.

00:17:06.306 --> 00:17:08.226
Jesus paid the price for you to be healed.

00:17:09.213 --> 00:17:16.120
We call you healed and whole and well in the name of Jesus.

00:17:16.120 --> 00:17:21.586
Now, Satan, take your hands off of God's property!

00:17:38.133 --> 00:17:44.554
We command you to release them now in Jesus' name.

00:17:50.406 --> 00:17:50.720
We break Strait satanic strongholds.

00:17:55.822 --> 00:17:56.284
We break addictions.

00:18:01.250 --> 00:18:06.893
We command them to be broken by Your power, by the blood that set us free.

00:18:06.893 --> 00:18:10.800
Whom the Son has set free is free indeed.

00:18:10.800 --> 00:18:18.560
I command healing, wholeness, and wellness over them in the name of Jesus.

00:18:31.665 --> 00:18:32.195
We thank You, Lord, that no bondage is on them from the top of their head to the soles of their feet.

00:18:32.195 --> 00:18:38.640
Now faith is the substance of things hoped for and evidence of things not seen.

00:18:38.640 --> 00:18:45.159
We call you healed now in Jesus' name.

00:18:45.159 --> 00:18:52.075
Faith calls those things that be not as though they were.

00:18:52.075 --> 00:18:55.834
We call you healed, well, and delivered.

00:18:55.834 --> 00:19:00.600
We call your marriages restored, healed, and whole.

00:19:00.600 --> 00:19:08.872
We call for a refreshing over the children, a fresh drink of Your living water over them.

00:19:08.872 --> 00:19:14.080
Father, let them realize that You're good and Your mercy endures forever.

00:19:14.080 --> 00:19:19.010
Great is Your faithfulness to them, O God.

00:19:19.010 --> 00:19:23.085
Nothing's too big for You to handle.

00:19:23.085 --> 00:19:26.089
Father, I thank You for Your mercy.

00:19:32.446 --> 00:19:32.943
I thank You that Your mercies are new every morning.

00:19:32.943 --> 00:19:46.120
They may think, 'I'm an old wretched sinner just saved by grace,' but Father, I thank You that You've saved them and delivered them.

00:19:46.120 --> 00:19:52.506
Give them a confidence of who they are in Christ Jesus.

00:19:52.506 --> 00:20:03.800
Let the eyes of their understanding be enlightened that they would know the hope of Your calling.

00:20:03.800 --> 00:20:12.559
Father, I thank You that they are not beat down with sin anymore; they are set free by Your blood and by the word of their testimony.

00:20:13.190 --> 00:20:21.013
I thank You, Holy Spirit, that You're ministering to them right now, showing them how special they really are.

00:20:21.013 --> 00:20:27.773
Jesus, You paid the price for them for love, joy, and peace.

00:20:27.773 --> 00:20:36.000
You said, 'Peace I leave with you; my peace I give to you.

00:20:36.000 --> 00:20:38.200
' Your Shalom peace.

00:20:54.700 --> 00:20:55.090
We receive that peace that passes all understanding by faith over our households.

00:20:56.080 --> 00:21:00.199
We receive joy—joy unspeakable and full of Your glory.

00:21:00.199 --> 00:21:07.795
We take authority over the spirit of depression right now in the name of Jesus.

00:21:19.503 --> 00:21:20.000
I command it to break off of them.

00:21:20.000 --> 00:21:24.590
We call the serotonin levels to be normal.

00:21:24.590 --> 00:21:27.760
We call their dopamine levels to be normal.

00:21:27.760 --> 00:21:31.360
We call their hormones to line up in their body.

00:21:31.360 --> 00:21:39.409
I call their brain to function like it's supposed to and fire like it's supposed to.

00:21:39.409 --> 00:21:42.819
Be whole, be healed, be well in Jesus' name.

00:21:42.819 --> 00:21:48.840
We speak to the serotonin levels to be normal in the large and small intestine.

00:21:54.823 --> 00:21:55.137
You said, 'Be anxious for nothing.

00:21:55.137 --> 00:22:03.331
' Take the care out of your prayer; we will take no care.

00:22:03.331 --> 00:22:17.776
Not only do we take the care out of our prayer, but Father, we are yielded and grounded in love because we realize my Father loves me.

00:22:17.776 --> 00:22:23.120
If my Father loves me, He's got me.

00:22:23.120 --> 00:22:24.930
He's protecting me.

00:22:24.930 --> 00:22:27.154
My Father loves me.

00:22:27.154 --> 00:22:34.340
Just practice that today; say it all day: 'My Father loves me.

00:22:34.340 --> 00:22:43.311
' You may feel like you're too far gone, but I'm telling you, perfect love casts out all fear.

00:22:52.720 --> 00:22:52.920
Get that love down inside of you.

00:22:52.920 --> 00:22:56.733
Say that all day: 'My Father loves me.

00:22:56.733 --> 00:22:58.400
Jesus loves me.

00:22:58.400 --> 00:23:02.705
' You've got to speak to your mountain.

00:23:10.800 --> 00:23:11.200
Your mountain has to hear your voice.

00:23:12.747 --> 00:23:15.879
Your voice has an address in the spirit realm.

00:23:31.268 --> 00:23:31.720
You've got to decree that out of your mouth, and you speak to your circumstances and they will change.

00:23:31.720 --> 00:23:38.680
I say it all the time: 'I am anointed to prosper.

00:23:38.680 --> 00:23:48.440
I have the ability to get wealth—not just to hoard it, but to be a blessing to others.

00:23:48.440 --> 00:23:53.253
' My Father has the cattle on a thousand hills.

00:23:57.724 --> 00:23:58.107
I speak blessing and increase over my finances.

00:23:58.107 --> 00:24:05.540
I have a supernatural ability to create wealth for my home.

00:24:07.990 --> 00:24:10.146
I say it all the time.

00:24:10.146 --> 00:24:15.853
The Lord is my shepherd, I shall not want.

00:24:15.853 --> 00:24:19.251
He leads me beside still waters.

00:24:19.251 --> 00:24:22.270
I will lack no good thing.

00:24:22.270 --> 00:24:26.143
I'm a tither, and I have tithers' rights.

00:24:26.143 --> 00:24:35.453
The blessing is on my house, the blessing is on my dogs, the blessing is on whatever I put my hands to.

00:24:35.453 --> 00:24:39.066
He said whatever I put my hands to prospers.

00:24:39.066 --> 00:24:40.898
We prosper in everything.

00:24:56.387 --> 00:24:56.742
We will be the head and not the tail, above and not beneath.

00:24:56.742 --> 00:25:00.320
You've got to start saying those things.

00:25:00.320 --> 00:25:06.559
You've got to believe it and quote that out of your mouth.

00:25:16.160 --> 00:25:16.360
It might not happen overnight, but faith calls those things that be not as though they were.

00:25:25.052 --> 00:25:25.306
You keep speaking to it and you're going to see that ship turn around.

00:25:27.668 --> 00:25:36.509
A big cruise ship takes a long time to turn, but you're going to turn that boat around—and it's not going to sink like the Titanic.

00:25:36.509 --> 00:25:42.364
You are going to change your circumstances by what you say out of your mouth.

00:25:42.364 --> 00:25:46.240
Life and death are in the power of your tongue.

00:25:46.240 --> 00:25:54.554
What you've been saying out of your mouth is what you're living today and what you're going to live tomorrow.

00:25:54.554 --> 00:25:58.079
But you start speaking good things.

00:25:58.079 --> 00:26:04.404
Life and death are in the power of your tongue—not in mine, in yours.

00:26:04.404 --> 00:26:11.200
That means you have the ability to create life or death with your words.

00:26:15.897 --> 00:26:23.800
You might be speaking all kinds of bad things: 'My husband's no good; he's a drunk, his daddy was a drunk, and he's always going to be a drunk.

00:26:23.800 --> 00:26:28.373
' Or 'They're always going to be on drugs.

00:26:28.373 --> 00:26:36.666
' What are you saying out of your mouth?

00:26:36.666 --> 00:26:42.023
'I'm never going to be healed, never going to be free.

00:26:42.023 --> 00:26:50.025
' That's what you're going to have because you are speaking into your life and reaping what you're sowing.

00:26:50.025 --> 00:26:58.010
You've got to sow good things and you're going to start seeing good things in your life.

00:26:58.010 --> 00:27:06.200
Most people don't want to hear that, but you are a product of what you've said over the years or what somebody has spoken over you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
Some people have been living under word curses.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
You've got to speak to those word curses and say, 'I condemn those words.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
You won't curse me.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.250
' Every tongue that rises against me, I condemn it; they fall to the ground.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
I will not allow that word to bear fruit in my life.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.800
You will not curse me with your mouth.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
Word curses, witches, warlocks—it goes back on you like a boomerang.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.750
It doesn't come on me.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
I'm blessed.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
You can't curse whom God has blessed.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
I walk in the blessing and the favor of the Lord.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.200
